==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Whorish
<hw>Whor"ish</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Resembling a whore in
character or conduct; addicted to unlawful pleasures; incontinent; lewd;
unchaste.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Whor"ish*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Whor"ish*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Whorl</ent>⟦br⟧
